\begin_layout Theorem
设间断面 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

 上任意一点的运动速度为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vec{s}=\vec{e}_{\nu}s_{\nu}+\vec{e}_{\tau}s_{\tau}
\]

\end_inset

其中 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{e}_{\nu}$
\end_inset

 与 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{e}_{\tau}$
\end_inset

 分别为该点处的“单位法向量”与“单位切向量”，则满足守恒律 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:微分方程：守恒律：方程组：动体"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 的守恒变量 
\begin_inset Formula $\ket{U}$
\end_inset

 及通量 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{\ket{F}}$
\end_inset

 在间断面 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

 两侧的值满足如下“跳跃条件 (jump condition)”（又名“Rankine–Hugoniot 条件”
\begin_inset Index idx
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
condition!jump ~!RankineHugoniot@Rankine–Hugoniot's ~
\end_layout

\end_inset

